This is just another proof that during the regular season, there is really no solid guarantee for any team, regardless of standings. A one-night game can see a bottom.team upsetting a top team or vi e versa.
Of course teams will still work hard enough to enter the playoffs...
However, when the 7-gane series comes along...we enter a totally different & exciting world of basketball.
This is when they will call for Regrouping, Urgency, Full-Force, & Vital Adjustments!
A team becomes an NBA Champs out of literal & figurative BLOOD, SWEAT & TEARS!
Looking fwd to The Playoffs.

While there might have been  the possibility that ANTHONY DAVIS somewhat rusty on his return, what happened during this game is more than a mighty WIN for the CELTICS; it is a rude awakening for pundits and those who believe the ALWAYS have the answers!
